ReadAbsentParent
data.value: select top(1) count(*) from CKT_CASE_ROLE where (START_DATE <= @startDate) and (END_DATE >= @startDate) and (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER)

data.name: ReadAbsentParentCsePerson1
data.value: select top(1) T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T2.TYPE, T2.FAMILY_VIOL_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON T2 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 on (T2.NUMB = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (@casNumber = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T1.END_DATE >= @startDate)

data.name: ReadAbsentParentCsePerson2
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T2.TYPE, T2.FAMILY_VIOL_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON T2 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 on (@casNumber = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.NUMB = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T1.END_DATE >= @startDate)

data.name: ReadCase
data.value: select top(1) NUMB from CKT_CASE where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadCaseAssignment
data.value: select top(1) REASON_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE where (@casNo = CAS_NO) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (REASON_CODE = 'RSP')

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, OTHER_STATE_CAS_ID, OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS, CASE_TYPE, KS_CASE_IND, OTH_STATE_CLS_RES, OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE, CAS_I_NUMBER, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_ID, COUNTRY from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST where (@casINumber = CAS_I_NUMBER) and (@croId = CRO_ID) and (@croType = CRO_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD = @othrStateFipsCd) and (OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD > 0)

data.name: ReadOffice
data.value: select top(1) OFFICE_ID, OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE where OFFICE_ID = @officeId

data.name: ReadOfficeCaseloadAssignment1
data.value: select top(1) OFCE_CSLD_ASSGN_ID, ENDING_ALPHA, BEGINING_ALPHA, EFFECTIVE_DATE, PRIORITY, DISCONTINUE_DATE, OFF_GENERATED_ID, OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, OSP_ROLE_CODE, END_FIRST_INITIAL, BGN_FIRST_INTIAL, ASSIGNMENT_IND, [FUNCTION], ASSIGNMENT_TYPE, OFF_D_GENERATED_ID, SPD_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFCE_CSLD_ASGT where (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (ASSIGNMENT_TYPE = 'RE') and (OFF_GENERATED_ID = 21) order by PRIORITY desc

data.name: ReadOfficeCaseloadAssignment2
data.value: select OFCE_CSLD_ASSGN_ID, ENDING_ALPHA, BEGINING_ALPHA, EFFECTIVE_DATE, PRIORITY, DISCONTINUE_DATE, OFF_GENERATED_ID, OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, OSP_ROLE_CODE, END_FIRST_INITIAL, BGN_FIRST_INTIAL, ASSIGNMENT_IND, [FUNCTION], ASSIGNMENT_TYPE, OFF_D_GENERATED_ID, SPD_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFCE_CSLD_ASGT where (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (ASSIGNMENT_TYPE = 'RE') and (BEGINING_ALPHA <= cast(@text6 as char(6))) and (ENDING_ALPHA >= cast(@text6 as char(6))) and (OFF_GENERATED_ID = 21) order by PRIORITY

data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProvider1
data.value: select top(1) T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.ROLE_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T1 join CKT_OFCE_CSLD_ASGT T2 on (T1.ROLE_CODE = T2.OSP_ROLE_CODE) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T2.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE) and (T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T2.OFF_D_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.OFCE_CSLD_ASSGN_ID = @ofceCsldAssgnId)

data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProvider2
data.value: select top(1) SPD_GENERATED_ID, OFF_GENERATED_ID, ROLE_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR where (EFFECTIVE_DATE = @effectiveDate1) and (ROLE_CODE = @roleCode) and (OFF_GENERATED_ID = @offGeneratedId) and (SPD_GENERATED_ID = @spdGeneratedId) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate2) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate2)

data.name: ReadServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, USER_ID from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER where SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = @servicePrvderId
